<template>
  <n-result
    status="404"
    title="404 服务器娘受不了跑路了"
    description="你们这样压榨是不人道的"
  >
    <template #footer>
      <template>
        <n-popconfirm
          @positive-click="handlePositiveClick"
          @negative-click="handleNegativeClick"
        >
          <template #trigger>
            <n-button>引用</n-button>
          </template>
          一切都将一去杳然，任何人都无法将其捕获。
        </n-popconfirm>
      </template>
    </template>
  </n-result>
</template>

<script>
import { defineComponent } from "vue";

export default defineComponent({
  setup() {
    function handleClick() {
      window.open("https://res.kcn3388.club/music.html", "_blank");
    }
    return {
      handleClick,
    };
  },
});
</script>
